dryrun demo

Procedure:
1) Estop-off  (F1)
2) Machine-on (F2)
3) Home-All   (Ctrl-Home)
4) Control using virtual panel:
      DRYRUN
        Start
        Stop
5) Observe Preview displays
   and
   Halshow Displays
---------------------------------------

This demo uses a pyvcp panel and
postgui file:
  dryrun_postgui.hal
  dryrun.xml

For a simple test without panels,
use commandline tools:

$ sim_pin \
    motion.dryrun-start/mode=Pulse \
    motion.dryrun-stop/mode=Pulse &

$ halmeter pin motion.is-dryrun &

---------------------------------------
Or add the following stanza to an existing
ini file.
[APPLICATIONS]
DELAY=5
APP = sim_pin motion.dryrun-start/mode=Pulse \
              motion.dryrun-stop/mode=Pulse

APP = halmeter pin motion.is-dryrun
